Aim
To design a responsive dashboard layout using CSS Grid.

Algorithm
STEP 1 : Create the basic HTML structure for the dashboard. 
STEP 2 : Divide the layout into header, sidebar, and content area. 
STEP 3 : Apply CSS Grid to the main container. 
STEP 4 : Define grid rows, columns, and areas. 
STEP 5 : Design the header section. 
STEP 6 : Create the sidebar navigation menu. 
STEP 7 : Design the main content area using cards. 
STEP 8 : Apply styles such as colors and spacing. 
STEP 9 : Test responsiveness using media queries.

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Grid Dashboard</title>

  <style>
    /* ===== RESET ===== */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f4f6f8;
    }

    /* ===== MAIN DASHBOARD GRID ===== */
    .dashboard {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 64px 1fr;
      grid-template-areas:
        "sidebar header"
        "sidebar main";
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ===== HEADER ===== */
    .header {
      grid-area: header;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 0 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    /* ===== SIDEBAR ===== */
    .sidebar {
      grid-area: sidebar;
      background: #111827;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .sidebar ul {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .sidebar li {
      padding: 12px 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .sidebar li:hover {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    /* ===== MAIN CONTENT ===== */
    .main {
      grid-area: main;
      padding: 24px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    /* ===== STAT CARDS ===== */
    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    /* ===== CONTENT GRID ===== */
    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .panel {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      min-height: 200px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .panel.large {
      grid-row: span 2;
    }

    /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .dashboard {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        grid-template-areas:
          "header"
          "main";
      }

      .sidebar {
        display: none;
      }

      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="dashboard">

    <aside class="sidebar">
      <ul>
        <li>Dashboard</li>
        <li>Analytics</li>
        <li>Users</li>
        <li>Settings</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>

    <header class="header">
      <h1>Dashboard</h1>
      <div>ðŸ‘¤ jan</div>
    </header>

    <main class="main">
      <section class="cards">
        <div class="card">Revenue</div>
        <div class="card">Users</div>
        <div class="card">Sessions</div>
        <div class="card">Conversions</div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-grid">
        <div class="panel large">Chart Area</div>
        <div class="panel">Recent Activity</div>
        <div class="panel">Notifications</div>
      </section>
    </main>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
